OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cloudy day, with outbreaks of
OL,6,Frain, mostly for southern Home
OL,7,FCounties. Turning drier for most away
OL,8,Ffrom Kent later in the day. A brisk
OL,9,Fnortheasterly wind, strong near
OL,10,Fcoasts, feeling cool.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FBecoming dry with late
OL,13,Fevening sunny spells as winds ease. A
OL,14,Fclear and cold night, with light winds
OL,15,Fand frost patches.
OL,16,
OL,17,CMonday:FIncreasingly cloudy, with a
OL,18,Fspell of rain through the middle of
OL,19,Fthe day. Largely dry and bright with
OL,20,Fsunny intervals later. Breezy and
OL,21,Ffeeling cool.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
